events.name: The Disappearance of Brandon Swanson
events.description: Brandon Swanson's vanishing without a trace in rural Minnesota remains a baffling mystery. According to his parents, during a 47-minute phone call, Brandon reported being shaken and disoriented after his car went off the road. Witnesses report seeing no signs of struggle or damage to the vehicle. However, it was unclear what exactly happened to Brandon as he failed to arrive home. Despite an extensive investigation by local authorities and searching parties in the surrounding area, no definitive evidence has been found. The case remains unexplained, with many speculating about potential explanations such as a medical emergency or even foul play. Ultimately, the true nature of Brandon's disappearance continues to be shrouded in mystery.

events.description: A remarkable sighting of a globular UFO was reported by a train passenger on May 25, 2025, at Junction 12 of the M25 in Surrey, England. According to the account, a woman sent her husband this video, which shows a bright, glowing craft hovering near the train tracks before disappearing into thin air. The eyewitness claims she's '100% positive' it wasn't a balloon. While witnesses report that the UFO was described as having no discernible shape or color, its behavior remains unexplained. Despite efforts to verify the sighting through US military channels, no conclusive evidence has been found. This case highlights the importance of approaching UFO reports with a critical and open-minded perspective.
